Package: thermgRad
Title: Tools to Visualize and Analyze Germination in Temperature Gradient Plates
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Pablo", "Gomez Barreiro", , "pablogomezbr@hotmail.es", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3140-3326"))
Description: Provides with tools to visualize and analyze germination experiments conducted using a temperature gradient plate (TGP) with a bidirectional setting (day/night cycle) and obtain cardinal temperatures for each of the temperature fluctuations thresholds across the thermal gradient plate.
